snippet.title: Krek Da Frog | Trailer 4k
snippet.description:
Funny and relaxing game, player can control the frog he choose in menu and eat butterflies, red butterflies are poisonous so if player eats them, he will loose one of his 3 lifes, if player has 0 lifes, game is over. To achieve all achievements player must eat at least 500 butterflies.


RELEASE DATE:
20-02-2022


#GameTrailers #Games #GoodGames
